			"editorData": {
				"HowToTrigger": {
					"type": 23,
					"value": "- Load up GustavDev/CTY_Main_A\r\n- Use \"oe MT_Start\", enter the tombstone shop and go down into the Murder Tribunal\r\n- Use \"oe MT_Dolor_Assault_Cheats\" to get Dolor to appear at the Death Knight guarding the courtroom. He will start attacking the Death Knight and will then turn his attention to the Murder Tribunal.\r\n- Once Sarevok is in combat with Dolor, Sarevok will say this AD and smite Dolor (if we are using cheats, his health is significantly boosted and he will survive the power word Kill, and the AD will repeat on Sarevok's every turn."
				},
